CatDescriptText: Front row, from left: Mr. Morris, Mr. Dimpsey, George Gilbert, John McCoy, Mr. Henry, Mr. Scott; back row: Alvin Rogers, Matthew Dimpsey, Claude Smith, Bill "Jitney Bean" McDaniel, Jethro McCoy, Sidney Pyle, and Mr. Phelps.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of thirteen men wearing Masonic aprons, including one seated front center wearing chain collar, gathered in interior with light colored walls
